{"tid":259272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鹹濕蟹】誤以為係生蠔 坡妹沙灘裸曬被螃蟹夾傷下體","createTime":"2017-05-26T18:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T03:52:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":146,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52e0cdbce9bf8e26520c6116121efd6727d91a72","tid":259272,"uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>【鹹濕蟹】誤以為係生蠔 坡妹沙灘裸曬被螃蟹夾傷下體</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時國際  2017-05-27 01:12:28 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n新加坡一名女子，偷偷在樟宜海灘裸體日光浴時，下體被一隻螃蟹夾傷，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">專家認為螃蟹可能誤以為那是生蠔而施襲</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n該名28歲女子，日前與兩名女友人到沙灘曬太陽，並趁四下無人時，把衣服脫光，盡情享受日光浴。曬了15分鐘後，該女子突覺下體劇痛，一望之下，驚見一隻大螃蟹用鉗夾著她下體不放，不禁大叫。她的朋友見狀，立即把蟹拿走，為她的傷口進行初步治理，待醫護人員到場。<br />\n<br />\n該女子傷勢無甚大礙，傷口很快復原，疤痕也不明顯，但心理創傷可能需要多點時間才可平復。新加坡法例禁止在沙灘上裸體，醫護人員也勸告傷者以後不要再裸曬。<br />\n<br />\n一名海洋生物學家說，螃蟹攻擊女性私處，是因為誤以為那是生蠔。他又說，蟹鉗一般無毒，但若被夾地方很敏感，可能出現過敏反應。"},{"pid":"6f2171a27f80913f3de6c92f27ce2062a92b2226","tid":259272,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317be37fad60ff4391619511bddd60e3ad0781e2","tid":259272,"uid":11639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa981362b07300430319a2b3b90b0929bcff913","tid":259272,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r